ActOther Than Statutory Authority
PrecisAppointment of EVAN FRIESENHAN of Edmonton, Alberta, a duly qualified engineer and Manager, Engineering Services – West and North, Meteorological Service of Canada, National Hydrological Services at Environment Canada, to be the Canadian accredited officer to carry out the provisions of the Treaty with respect to the St. Mary and Milk Rivers, to hold office during pleasure.
